message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which we believe is worth more than $80. Would you like to make an offer?
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of your product. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $85.
Thank you for your counteroffer, Bob. We appreciate your interest in our product. We would like to counter with an offer of $90 for the product.
I understand Alice, thank you for your counteroffer. I would like to propose a counteroffer of $87.
